ompleted all of them in one day.\"'),(5803,86,2,41,0,'\"Young Bétamarribé boy from Koaba with a slingshot around his neck. The scar patterns cut into the faces of Bétamarribé men resemble the intricate structure of a finely woven textile. One-hundred years ago, men selected one or two symbols from their scar patterns and placed them on their belongings so that they would serve as personal property marks.\"\r\n'),(5802,86,2,49,0,'Benin, 21st Century, cultural'),(4205,58,3,74,0,'8'),(4206,58,3,75,0,'3'),(4207,58,3,77,0,'a:9:{s:8:\"FileName\";s:36:\"0279515768d01375faf3715d593d9f1d.jpg\";s:12:\"FileDateTime\";i:1352578182;s:8:\"FileSize\";i:15679;s:8:\"FileType\";i:2;s:8:\"MimeType\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:13:\"SectionsFound\";s:5:\"APP12\";s:8:\"COMPUTED\";a:4:{s:4:\"html\";s:24:\"width=\"175\" height=\"246\"\";s:6:\"Height\";i:246;s:5:\"Width\";i:175;s:7:\"IsColor\";i:1;}s:7:\"Company\";s:5:\"Ducky\";s:4:\"Info\";s:1:\"\";}'),(4208,58,3,76,0,'FileName:0279515768d01375faf3715d593d9f1d.jpg\nFileDateTime:1352578182\nFileSize:15679\nFileType:2\nMimeType:image/jpeg\nSectionsFound:APP12\nCOMPUTED:\n	html:width=\"175\" height=\"246\"\n	Height:246\n	Width:175\n	IsColor:1\n\nCompany:Ducky\nInfo:\n'),(4209,58,3,73,0,'246'),(4210,58,3,72,0,'175'),(6047,89,2,40,0,'2002'),(6048,89,2,47,0,'Lars Krutak'),(6049,89,2,46,0,'Unknown'),(6050,89,2,42,0,'JPEG'),(6051,89,2,51,0,'Image'),(6052,89,2,43,0,'Unknown'),(6053,89,2,38,0,'<kml xmlns=\"http://earth.google.com/kml/2.0\"><Folder><name>OpenLayers export</name><description>Exported on Sat Nov 10 2012 15:22:52 GMT-0800 (PST)</description><Placemark><name>OpenLayers.Feature.Vector_160</name><description>No description available</description><Point><coordinates>277569.92116087,1192467.679579</coordinates></Point></Placemark></Folder></kml>|5|639575.68706907|859813.73252816|ghyb\r\nAfrica'),(6054,89,2,7,0,'Photo'),(6055,89,2,10,0,'175 x 246'),(4224,59,3,74,0,'8'),(4225,59,3,75,0,'3'),(4226,59,3,77,0,'a:9:{s:8:\"FileName\";s:36:\"e3a5c265b6