me to symbolize toughness and boost the confidence of egotistical males.  The document further explains the influence of these actions and this disposition on American culture, economy, and politics.'),(9861,189,3,74,0,'8'),(9862,189,3,73,0,'389'),(9863,189,3,72,0,'642'),(9864,171,2,50,0,'Modern Day Samoan Tatau'),(9865,171,2,49,0,'Samoa/America - 21st century - Cultural'),(9866,171,2,41,1,'This video depicts the traditional method of Samoan tatau being performed in modern day by Seymour Kahiliaulani Kaniho-Lindsey. He is a world-renowned tattoo artist and is a firm believer in preserving the traditions of his culture. Using the au tools, he taps the ink in to the skin one spot at a time. He is one of the few tattoo artists in America to provide the traditional Pe\'a tatau through the original methods. <iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/4oI8_P5YiaY\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\"></iframe>'),(9867,171,2,39,0,'Seymour Kahiliaulani Kaniho-Lindsey'),(9868,171,2,45,0,'Richie Merritt YouTube Channel'),(9869,171,2,40,0,'2012'),(9870,171,2,38,0,'<kml xmlns=\"http://earth.google.com/kml/2.0\"><Folder><name>OpenLayers export</name><description>Exported on Thu Nov 29 2012 18:53:34 GMT-0800 (PST)</description><Placemark><name>OpenLayers.Feature.Vector_159</name><description>No description available</description><Point><coordinates>-13115371.059458,3970503.1751787</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>OpenLayers.Feature.Vector_169</name><description>No description available</description><Point><coordinates>-19193643.547849,-1526970.6155862</coordinates></Point></Placemark></Folder></kml>|2|-15908074.324496|963898.05248537|ghyb\r\n'),(9890,190,3,74,0,'8'),(9891,190,3,73,0,'657'),(9892,190,3,72,0,'982'),(9904,191,3,74,0,'8'),(9905,191,3,73,0,'293'),(9906,191,3,72,0,'161'),(10004,154,2,49,0,'United States, 21st century, cultural'),(9987,169,2,43,0,'Unknown'),(9986,169,2,51,0,'PDF'),(9983,169,2,46,0,'Unknown'),(9984,169,2,42,0,'PDF'),(9985,169,2